desc: Calypso Boats is the manufacture of the Legendary Caribbean Boats like the Calypso 23, Calypso 28 and the unmatched Calypso 34 (aka- Super Panga!) We also build several Deep Vee boats ranging from 26 to 39 feet that have also become legendary over the past 20 years for their off shore performance.

layout.text: The legendary CALYPSO34 reimagined for today's applications
